name: Tharja - Fire Emblem: Awakening (Character)
description:
This is a LORA of the character Tharja from the Intelligent Systems SRPG Fire Emblem: Awakening

To prompt this character, enter "<lora:Tharjav1:strength>Tharja, gold-lined bodystocking, gold loincloth, hair ornament, cape,,". Can be prompted with a light 3D aesthetic from Fire Emblem Warriors using "3D Model".

This LORA looks the best at 0.6 ~ 0.8 strength in my opinion. Tharja was trained on AnythingElsev4.5 at Clip Skip 2.
